  "title": "M&E Engineer [Building proj]/ 5day/Upto $7K+VB/ A1 Maincon MNC/ West",
  "description": "<ul><li><li><p><strong>Up to Basic $7,000 + Bonus + Benefits</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>M&E Engineer or Senior Engineer/ Permanent position/ 5 workdays/ Jurong East area</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Experience in working in main contractor is mandatory. </strong></p></li></li></ul><p><strong>Our client is a reputable MNC and leading A1 main contractor diverse in civil and infrastructure project.</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><li><p>Assist the M&E Manager in coordinating M&E works at site</p></li><li><p>Planning, Scheduling and coordination of site M&E service works. </p></li><li><p>Reviewing M&E Shop Drawing , project supervision and documentation submission for approval</p></li><li><p>Manage and liaise with M&E subcontractor on M&E work progress on schedule. </p></li><li><p>Compliance with all necessary standards, code of practice and safety regulations</p></li></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Mechanical or Electrical Engineering or its equivalent</li><li>Experience in design and building projects is mandatory.</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p><p><strong>To apply please click on the APPLY NOW button or email your resume to </strong><a href=\"mailto:search84@searchindex.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>search84@searchindex.com.sg</strong></a><strong> with the following detail:</strong></p><ul><li>Reason for leaving each past & current employment</li><li>Salary drawn for each past & current employment</li><li>Expected Salary</li><li>Earliest availability date</li></ul><p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p><p><strong>Lionel Cheow</strong></p><p><strong>EA License | 14C7092</strong></p><p><strong>EA Registration Number | R1105005</strong></p>",
